<module status="bronze">
    <h>cuir</h>
    <p><g>cuir</g>
        <en>put, send</en> is a <a href="?xx=verbs/simple_verbs">simple verb</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>cuir</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>cuiridh</m> – future independent, i.e. <en>will put</en></li>
                <li><m>chuir</m> – past independent, i.e. <en>put</en></li>
                <li><m>cur</m> – verbal noun, i.e. <en>putting</en></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section>
            <h>tense</h>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>past <ul id="past">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>chuir</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>chuir</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do chuir</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>chuireadh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>chuireadh</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do chuireadh</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>future <ul id="future">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>cuiridh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>chuireas</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha <m>chuir</m>, an/nach <m>cuir</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>cuirear</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>chuirear</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha <m>chuirear</m>, an/nach <m>cuirear</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>conditional <ul id="conditional">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>first person singular <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>chuirinn</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>chuirinn</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha <m>chuirinn</m>, an/nach
                                                  <m>cuirinn</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>first person plural <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>chuireamaid</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>chuireamaid</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha <m>chuireamaid</m>, an/nach
                                                  <m>cuireamaid</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>second/third persons <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>chuireadh</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>chuireadh</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha <m>chuireadh</m>, an/nach
                                                  <m>cuireadh</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>chuirte</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>chuirte</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha <m>chuirte</m>, an/nach <m>cuirte</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
